\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I need to set the stage here\'85Saul is using the bathroom in the same cave that David and his men are hiding.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is not a good situation for King Saul to have the man you are trying to hunt down and kill is right behind you while you have your pants down.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
