\f0\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 4\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The men said, \'93This is the day the Lord\'a0spoke\'a0of when he said
\fs15 \super [\ul b\ulnone ]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0to you, \'91I will give your enemy into your hands for you to deal with as you wish.\'92\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
