\f0\b\fs18 \super 6\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He said to his men, \'93The\'a0Lord\'a0forbid that I should do such a thing to my master, the\'a0Lord\'92s anointed,\'a0or lay my hand on him; for he is the anointed of the\'a0Lord.\'94\'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 7\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub With these words David sharply rebuked his men and did not allow them to attack Saul. And Saul left the cave and went his way.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}David let him go\'85he didn\'92t pull the trigger.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Just because it looks like a God things, and feels like a God thing, and your friends around you tell you it\'92s a God thing, doesn\'92t mean it is a God thing.\
